[moses to mtplz converter]

!!!NOTE!!! This program is an alpha version. !!!NOTE!!!

This program converts the configurations and phrase tables of Moses decoder into mtplz decoder.
Moses decoder: https://github.com/moses-smt/mosesdecoder
mtplz: https://github.com/kpu/mtplz

* Usage
python m2m.py --ini moses.ini --decoder mtplz/bin/decode --output /path/to/output

After converting the configurations, run /path/to/output/mtplz_wrap.sh.
Note that:
stdin = foreign language sentences,
stdout = translated sentences, and,
stderr = logs of mtplz.

